Daily XP.

00:00:16.940 --> 00:00:22.649
The developer Poppermost today revealed an
exciting new open world winter sports MMO

00:00:22.649 --> 00:00:24.180
called SNOW.

00:00:24.180 --> 00:00:27.830
Well it's exciting if you're into sports and
going outside I guess.

00:00:27.830 --> 00:00:32.239
