exploring a massive mountain environment on

00:00:32.239 --> 00:00:33.350
either your ski or snowboard.

00:00:33.350 --> 00:00:38.269
There will be content for both casual and
competitive players as well as group and solo

00:00:38.269 --> 00:00:39.540
events and competitions.

00:00:39.540 --> 00:00:42.760
The Alpha for SNOW will hit later this year.

00:00:42.760 --> 00:00:46.670
